      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-stp-prn-mrk-uno      .
           move      spaces               to   w-stp-prn-mrk-beg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Inizializzazione area per rotture di livello    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-rot                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Inizializzazione flag di interruzione forzata   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-stp-prn-flg-int      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start iniziale                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   prn-str-ini-000      thru prn-str-ini-999        .
           if        w-stp-prn-flg-sub    not  = spaces
                     move   spaces        to   w-stp-prn-flg-sub
                     go to  prn-rou-pri-600.
       prn-rou-pri-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio area rottura in area precedente     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rot-l05            to   w-stp-prn-sav-l05      .
